title: The Infowarrior - Featuring Jason Bermas-5-6-09.Commercial Free.
description:
The Info Warrior Show(internet radio) with Jason Bermas May 6th,2009 from prisonplanet.tv - Commercial free. 64Kbps.mp3

Larry Pratt of Gun Owners of America Joins Jason in hour Number one to discuss the latest DHS document, and the FEMA NLE. Jason plays the Lou Dobbs "DHS Lexicon" clip where Congressman Pete King(Ranking member of The Homeland Security Committee) comments on "thought control".  The phone lines are open all night, as well.
